OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775585464
OL,3,CNew hospital land purchase complete
OL,4,Cdespite 10-year delay in construction
OL,6,FA new hospital looks set to be built
OL,7,Fafter the final piece of land was
OL,8,Fpurchased - despite the completion
OL,9,Fdate being pushed back by around 10
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FConstruction on the site - earmarked
OL,13,Ffor the new Royal Preston Hospital -
OL,14,Fwas originally due to begin in 2030
OL,15,Fand be completed by the middle of that
OL,16,Fdecade after the first section of land
OL,17,Fwas bought in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
