PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775585464
OL,3,CNew hospital land purchase complete
OL,4,Cdespite 10-year delay in construction
OL,6,FBut doors are now not expected to open
OL,7,Funtil the early-mid 2040s, after the
OL,8,Ftimeframe for building was brought
OL,9,Funder review by the new Labour
OL,10,Fgovernment.
OL,12,FLabour accused its Conservative
OL,13,Fpredecessors of failing to fund a
OL,14,Fcommitment to a claimed "40 new
OL,15,Fhospitals" nationwide - including
OL,16,FPreston.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
