FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775585464
OL,3,CNew hospital land purchase complete
OL,4,Cdespite 10-year delay in construction
OL,6,FThe government recently released the
OL,7,Ffunding for the land, off Stanifield
OL,8,FLane in the Farington area of South
OL,9,FRibble, as local NHS leaders announced
OL,10,Fthe provisional plot had been
OL,11,Facquired, the Local Democracy
OL,12,FReporting Service (LDRS) said.
OL,14,FIn January 2025, Health Secretary Wes
OL,15,FStreeting announced that the start
OL,16,Fdate for the scheme had been pushed
OL,17,Fback to between 2037 and 2039 `
OL,18,Fmeaning the new hospital would not be
OL,19,Ftreating patients for the best part of
OL,20,F20 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775585464
OL,3,CNew hospital land purchase complete
OL,4,Cdespite 10-year delay in construction
OL,6,FHowever, the NHS was permitted to draw
OL,7,Fdown the finance to secure the
OL,8,Fremaining part of the 64-acre site in
OL,9,FMarch 2026.
OL,11,FThat portion of the plot was owned by
OL,12,FLancashire County Council, which is
OL,13,Fdeveloping the 'Lancashire Central'
OL,14,Flogistics, retail and leisure hub on
OL,15,Fadjoining land.
OL,17,FThe amounts paid have not yet been
OL,18,Fmade publicly available. The cost
OL,19,Festimate for the overall hospital
OL,20,Fdevelopment was set at #2bn when it
OL,21,Fwas published almost 18 months ago.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
