CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775585464
OL,3,CNew hospital land purchase complete
OL,4,Cdespite 10-year delay in construction
OL,6,FThe NHS has stressed that any new site
OL,7,Fwould be subject to public
OL,8,Fconsultation before being confirmed.
OL,9,FPlanning permission would also be
OL,10,Frequired.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
